data.description: Lovely brand new home on 5+ acres in the beautiful Lost Creek area. Plenty of room  family and pets, horses are welcome. Unfinished basement will add more room, and equity to the home. High end finishes, and a huge and impressive master suite will make enjoyable living.Great room and loft, and master has vaulted ceilings, with great views out every window. Kitchen is absolutely adorable, a dream come true. There are water rights to irrigate the property. Come see this great new build, with room to run today!
